      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>While you wait</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>While you wait for something to happen </l>
          <l>While you wait for change to come </l>
          <l>While you change you go uncertain </l>
          <l>You certainly forget your tongue </l>
          <l>While you think your body ages </l>
          <l>When you age your thought is weakened </l>
          <l>All the week I bring you freedom </l>
          <l>You never bring me anything </l>
          <l>While you shout you cannot listen </l>
          <l>When you listen, patiently await your turn </l>
          <l>While you grow your life is changing </l>
          <l>You understand your thoughts were wrong</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
